This will test the next sequential release
Ensure Prompt=never then: sudo sed -i 's/Prompt=never/Prompt=normal/ (5)
Ensure Prompt=lts then: sudo sed -i 's/Prompt=lts/Prompt=normal/ (6)
Ensure sed command fails (7)
Ensure a new release is found (8)
Ensure asked to start the upgrade (9)
Ensure asked (10)
Ensure asked (11)
